relevant_communication:
- extensive work assisting journalists in covering the Cambridge Analytica and FB scandals; 
- testimony in several hearings of EU authorities (Digital Clearinghouse, EU Parliament, EDPS); 
- educational material around GDPR user rights; 
- training for journalists, activists and policy makers throughout Europe on data protection rights.

goals__remit:
Our goals are: 
- Increase awareness of issues relating to personal data and their use;  
- Ease the exercise of data protection rights; 
- Increase awareness of collective dimension of those issues; 
- Ease the exercise of data protection rights collectively; 
- Partner with other initiatives going into those directions.
